                        <!-- 题目与AI讲解区 -->
                        <div class="lg:col-span-1 p-6 max-h-[700px] overflow-y-auto scrollbar-hide">
                            <div class="mb-6">
                                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                                    <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full mr-2">入门</span>
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">A+B问题</h3>
                                    <span class="ml-auto text-sm text-gray-500">洛谷 P1001</span>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6 shadow-sm">
                                    <h4 class="font-medium mb-2">题目描述</h4>
                                    <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">输入两个整数a和b，输出它们的和。</p>
                                    
                                    <h4 class="font-medium mb-2">支持语言</h4>
                                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
                                        <span class="language-badge bg-c/10 text-c border border-c/20 text-[10px]">C</span>
                                        <span class="language-badge bg-cpp/10 text-cpp border border-cpp/20 text-[10px]">C++</span>
                                        <span class="language-badge bg-java/10 text-java border border-java/20 text-[10px]">Java</span>
                                        <span class="language-badge bg-python/10 text-python border border-python/20 text-[10px]">Python</span>
                                        <span class="language-badge bg-js/10 text-js border border-js/20 text-[10px]">JavaScript</span>
                                        <span class="language-badge bg-csharp/10 text-csharp border border-csharp/20 text-[10px]">C#</span>
                                        <span class="language-badge bg-go/10 text-go border border-go/20 text-[10px]">Go</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <!-- AI讲解区 -->
                            <div>
                                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                                    <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-2">
                                        <i class="fa fa-robot text-secondary"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">AI语言专属讲解</h3>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-sm mb-4">
                                    <div class="flex mb-3 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">
                                        <button class="language-tab active px-3 py-1 mr-2 rounded text-sm font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary">Python</button>
                                        <button class="language-tab px-3 py-1 mr-2 rounded text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-100">C++</button>
                                        <button class="language-tab px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-100">Java</button>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="language-content active">
                                        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                                            <p class="text-gray-700">在Python中，这道题非常简单，利用内置的input()函数和print()函数即可完成。</p>
                                            
                                            <p class="text-gray-700">Python解题特点：</p>
                                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                                                <li>无需声明变量类型，直接赋值即可</li>
                                                <li>input().split()可以方便地读取多个输入</li>
                                                <li>map(int, ...)用于类型转换</li>
                                                <li>print()函数自动添加换行</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="language-content hidden">
                                        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                                            <p class="text-gray-700">在C++中，需要包含iostream头文件，使用cin和cout进行输入输出操作。</p>
                                            
                                            <p class="text-gray-700">C++解题要点：</p>
                                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                                                <li>必须声明变量类型（int a, b）</li>
                                                <li>使用cin >> 读取输入，cout << 输出结果</li>
                                                <li>注意添加命名空间（using namespace std;）</li>
                                                <li>main函数需要返回0</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="language-content hidden">
                                        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                                            <p class="text-gray-700">在Java中，需要创建类和main方法，使用Scanner类进行输入操作。</p>
                                            
                                            <p class="text-gray-700">Java解题要点：</p>
                                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                                                <li>必须定义public class</li>
                                                <li>需要导入java.util.Scanner</li>
                                                <li>使用sc.nextInt()读取整数</li>
                                                <li>类名必须与文件名保持一致</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <button class="w-full py-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary border border-primary rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/5 transition-colors">
